#######
#ABOUT#
#######

This script is designed to kill Amazon EC2 instances that are over a certain age

#######
#USAGE#
#######

./killer.sh [kill hours] [warn hours]

eg

./killer.sh 72 48

This will terminate instances that were launched over 72 hours ago, and warn re. instances that were launched over 48 hours
ago

##############
#REQUIREMENTS#
##############

jsawk
https://github.com/micha/jsawk

Spidermonkey js interpreter
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Projects/SpiderMonkey

Script must be run from Amazon EC2 instanace which has IAM Role with permissions to Describe and Terminate instances
